{"tid":1009063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜年必備：長輩圖「精讀班」","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T13:22:37.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96178bb5215220d16fc36b609462ed4505162a7c","tid":1009063,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190204/s00001/3c4e9faf989fd8377d444c79141d2528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F3c4e9faf989fd8377d444c79141d2528.jpg&h=ddfc8e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n父系親戚：<br />\n爸爸的爸爸：爺爺<br />\n爸爸的媽媽：嫲嫲<br />\n爸爸的哥哥：伯伯<br />\n伯伯的太太：伯娘<br />\n爸爸的弟弟：叔叔<br />\n叔叔的太太：嬸嬸<br />\n爸爸的姐姐：姑媽<br />\n爸爸的妹妹：姑姐<br />\n姑媽和姑姐的丈夫：姑丈<br />\n爺爺的哥哥：伯爺<br />\n爺爺的弟弟：叔公<br />\n爺爺的姐妹：姑婆<br />\n嫲嫲的兄弟：舅公<br />\n嫲嫲的姐妹：姨婆<br />\n伯伯及叔叔的子女：堂兄弟姐妹<br />\n姑媽及姑姐的子女：表兄弟姐妹<br />\n<br />\n母系親戚：<br />\n媽媽的爸爸：公公<br />\n媽媽的媽媽：婆婆<br />\n媽媽的兄弟：舅父<br />\n媽媽的姐姐：姨媽<br />\n媽媽的妹妹：姨姨<br />\n公公的哥哥：外伯公<br />\n公公的弟弟：外叔公<br />\n公公的姐妹：外姑婆<br />\n婆婆的兄弟：外舅公<br />\n婆婆的姐妹：外姨婆<br />\n舅父的太太：舅母<br />\n姨媽和姨姨的丈夫：姨丈<br />\n舅父、姨媽及姨姨的子女：表兄弟姐妹<br />\n<br />\n以上為長輩及平輩稱呼。至於後輩，兄弟的兒女稱為「侄」；姐妹的兒子稱為「外甥」，女兒稱為「姨甥」；堂兄弟姊妹或表兄弟姊妹兒女，則分別在「侄」、「外甥」和「姨甥」前面加上「堂」或「表」。<br />\n<br />\n如仍有疑問，有人在網上製作「親戚稱呼計算機」，輸入指令助大家找出親戚稱謂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190204/s00001/1549295898941/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0%E3%80%91%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%85%E5%82%99-%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E5%9C%96%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%BE%E8%AE%80%E7%8F%AD%E3%80%8D-%E7%88%B8%E5%AA%BD%E8%A6%AA%E6%88%9A%E5%8F%AB%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F1549295898941%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%258B%259C%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E5%259C%2596%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E8%25AE%2580%25E7%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2588%25B8%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2588%259A%25E5%258F%25AB%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=33dbac6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F1549295898941%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%258B%259C%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E5%259C%2596%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E8%25AE%2580%25E7%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2588%25B8%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2588%259A%25E5%258F%25AB%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC&h=feda6621\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190204/s00001/1549295898941/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0%E3%80%91%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%85%E5%82%99-%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E5%9C%96%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%BE%E8%AE%80%E7%8F%AD%E3%80%8D-%E7%88%B8%E5%AA%BD%E8%A6%AA%E6%88%9A%E5%8F%AB%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC</a>"},{"pid":"fdb7f2830c9bc3b1bb83d2cf520388d8915ec570","tid":1009063,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"uncles aunties 搞掂 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d7dc07c29b414318ca8a320ff4c91145ea4b94","tid":1009063,"uid":159074,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"有app可以查<br />\nan ios都有<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JspZuOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJspZuOe.png&h=8b88a967&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f08a904a81dd504d43a8164bc0448621a4158735","tid":1009063,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"hi，搞掂"},{"pid":"de818fd95df0c63ec7abb5a33c2e33c877d3b25f","tid":1009063,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite